ygData.messageBody:
Correct, the latest server is The Nameless. I am currently on that server
(from Prexus) playing my first cleric and I must say it is fun. Starting out
on a new server with a class that groups love is the best grouping exp i've
ever had. I am currently lv 23 with the av newbie lvl being around 14 to 20.
There are a lot of 14 to 20's, but all the major dungeons lv 20 and up are
empty enuf to have HARDLY any trains and some VERY nice exp (excluding
unrest.. ppl like to solo the house there at lv 13.. where'd they get that
idea?) Places like Guk, Cazic Thule, Mistmoore, etc all have less then 10
ppl in them at a time.

If you want to start a new server i would highly suggest the Nameless. Even
has several gms on... tho not as many as other servers =\

Demius: Lv 23 Dwarf Cleric
